    packageLoadingDescription: "Loading description...",
    packageFallbackDescription: "An exciting jetski adventure! Contact us for more details.",
    package_seadoo_30_min_title: "SeaDoo Jetski 30 Minutes",
    package_seadoo_1_hr_title: "SeaDoo Jetski 1 Hour",
    package_seadoo_1_hr_batu_gantung_title: "1 Hour Jetski Tour to Batu Gantung",
    package_seadoo_2_hr_15_min_situmurun_title: "2 Hrs 15 Mins Jetski Tour to Situmurun Waterfall",
    package_batu_gantung_short_title: "Batu Gantung Package",
    package_situmurun_short_title: "Situmurun Waterfall Package",
    package_seadoo_30_min_summary: "A pure adrenaline shot for the instant thrill-seeker. Feel the power, command the waves, and create spectacular content in 30 minutes that will last forever.",
    package_seadoo_1_hr_summary: "A blank canvas for the soul that craves freedom. Explore hidden coves or race on open water in our most popular package. The only one that allows driver swaps!",
    package_seadoo_1_hr_batu_gantung_summary: "A pilgrimage across the water to Lake Toba's most mysterious icon. Hear the legend of Seruni and capture an epic photo against the unforgettable dramatic cliffs.",
    package_seadoo_2_hr_15_min_situmurun_summary: "The grandest expedition to a hidden gem of Lake Toba. Witness a waterfall plunging directly into the lake, swim at its confluence, and have a priceless, ultimate experience.",
    package_seadoo_30_min_desc: "<p><b>For the instant thrill-seeker.</b> Picture this: in a flash, you're blasting off from the dock, leaving all the noise behind. It's just you, a responsive SeaDoo engine, and the calling expanse of Lake Toba. This 30-minute session is a shot of pure adrenaline, designed to give you maximum happiness in minimum time.</p><p>This isn't just a short spin. It's a golden opportunity to become the star of your social media. Our documentation team will capture every smile, every sharp maneuver, and every epic splash. In an instant, you'll have spectacular content that will make everyone envious.</p><p>Feeling hesitant? Think of this as a 'warm-up' for a bigger adventure, or the perfect way to fill a break in your holiday with something unforgettable. Feel the power, command the waves, and create a memory in 30 minutes that will last forever.</p>",
    package_seadoo_1_hr_desc: "<p><b>For the soul that craves freedom.</b> One hour. Sixty minutes to forget the world and become the master of the waters of Lake Toba. This isn't just about speed; it's about the freedom to write your own adventure. Want to push the adrenaline on the open water? Go for it. Want to leisurely explore hidden coves? The world is yours.</p><p>This package is your blank canvas. With the ideal duration, you have time to truly connect with the jetski, feel every turn, and find your own rhythm on the water. It's our most popular package for a reason: the perfect balance of excitement and exploration.</p><p>And the best part? You can share this freedom. As our only non-tour package that allows for a driver swap, bring your partner or best friend along to feel the sensation. Create a story together, capture moments against the backdrop of Samosir's green hills, and let the lake witness your adventure.</p>",
    package_seadoo_1_hr_batu_gantung_desc: "<p><b>For the chaser of legends and dramatic views.</b> Forget for a moment about just riding. This tour is a pilgrimage across the water to one of Lake Toba's most mysterious and stunning icons. As you approach the majestic Batu Gantung cliff, you're not just seeing a rock formation; you're feeling the vibration of a legend passed down through generations.</p><p>Listen to the tragic tale of Seruni from our guide as you float beneath the towering cliff. Feel how the story brings the landscape around you to life. This is a moment where adrenaline meets cultural wonder, creating an experience that is deep and soul-stirring.</p><p>Our documentation team will be your personal director, ensuring you get a photo that is not only beautiful but also full of meaning. A portrait of you on a jetski with Batu Gantung in the background isn't just a vacation photo; it's proof that you have touched the heart of Lake Toba's story. This tour is for you who believe the best adventures always have a powerful story behind them.</p>",
    package_seadoo_2_hr_15_min_situmurun_desc: "<p><b>For the true adventurer who craves the unforgettable.</b> This is not a tour. This is an expedition. An epic journey that will take you far beyond the usual tourist routes, to a hidden gem of Lake Toba: the Situmurun Waterfall. Imagine the sensation: after crossing an endless expanse of blue water, you arrive at a secluded paradise where a powerful waterfall cascades directly from the cliff into the lake.</p><p>This is a multi-sensory experience. Feel its refreshing mist on your face, listen to its mighty roar, and witness a sight that many can only dream of. Turn off your jetski's engine, and let the majesty of nature take over. Swim in the cool, fresh water at its meeting point, a cleansing moment you will remember forever.</p><p>The journey itself is a gift, passing through quiet fishing villages and dramatic limestone cliffs. You will see the wild, pure, and untouched face of Lake Toba. If you are looking for the one thing that will be the pinnacle of your entire trip, the one story you will tell over and over again, this is it. Dare to have the best.</p>",
